'use strict';
 
// Queue class adapted from Tim Caswell's pattern library
// http://github.com/creationix/pattern/blob/master/lib/pattern/queue.js
 
function Queue() {
    this.tail = [];
    this.head = [];
    this.offset = 0;
}
